<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thepna achun lut kin, gitlohna ahi,
 Na zawhnan zozel din hun panpih ina;
 Hang takin do zelin, thim hatna zoin,
 Isu lam en zingin, hunpui zel ina.

[V2]
 Hukdampa panpih ngen in,
 Lungmuon, hihhat, hun veng di'n;
 Ama'n A hun panpih nuom,
 Nang hun pui zel ina.

[V3]
 2. Guol gilo nusie'n la, pau phalo mang ki'n,
 Pathien min zah inla, mawka suoh lo in;
 Lungnem, phachuom ngaiin lungthim dik takin,
 Isu lam en zingin, hun pui zel ina.

[V4]
 3. Pathien in guol zote Lallukhuk piena,
 Gin vangin zo hitiu, puk sek mahleu hing;
 I Hukdampau in hatna thak ei piena,
 Isu lam en zingin, hun pui zel ina.</lyrics>
<title>YIELD NOT TO TEMPTATION</title>
<hymn_number>311</hymn_number>
</song>